issue.title: Fix deleted mailbox bug
issue.body:
When deleting a mailbox manually from context.io console, the account with the associated mailbox stops working properly on the dashboard page specifically after throwing this **Blazer** error to the console:

```
Error: {{#each}} currently only accepts arrays, cursors or falsey values.
    at s (7ad2bf09c9434363eda313f66e11958cdaa85248.js:59)
    at 7ad2bf09c9434363eda313f66e11958cdaa85248.js:59
    at Object.t.nonreactive (7ad2bf09c9434363eda313f66e11958cdaa85248.js:15)
    at 7ad2bf09c9434363eda313f66e11958cdaa85248.js:59
    at t.Computation._compute (7ad2bf09c9434363eda313f66e11958cdaa85248.js:15)
    at t.Computation._recompute (7ad2bf09c9434363eda313f66e11958cdaa85248.js:15)
    at Object.t._runFlush (7ad2bf09c9434363eda313f66e11958cdaa85248.js:15)
    at e (7ad2bf09c9434363eda313f66e11958cdaa85248.js:3)
```

issue.title: Add Picture Mail
issue.body:
- Add a Mail Icon to the card content.
- Mail Icon should open Modal that loads the container email asynchronously.
- Opened Mail should contain button to load all images on that mail, to show them on the modal.
